
========================================
ECCO Sampling Tool: A Brief Description
========================================

What the Tool does: 
   The Tool extracts time-series of a user-defined variable of the
   ECCO estimate, V4r4. The Tool is useful for assessing the fidelity
   of this model. See
   PUBLICDIR/README
   for additional ECCO Modeling Utilities (EMU). 

How to run the Tool:
   Execute shell script emu_samp.csh and follow its prompt; e.g., 
   source PUBLICDIR/emu_samp.csh

For detailed description: 
   See Sections 1, 2.1, and 3.1 of the EMU User Guide; 
   PUBLICDIR/Guide_ECCO_Modeling_Utilities.pdf

========================================

